{
  "texts": [
    "The baseline function of this family of tools is to allow users to create and manipulate images based on text inputs.",
    "Certain products have additional offerings: Stability AI, for example, has also released GAI-powered tools that create music and sound effects and video.",
    "While these tools that generate images and other media are not marketed exclusively for teachers, researchers, or students, they are often included on lists of products that may find use in educational contexts.",
    "Researchers and students are also finding products that generate code useful.",
    "Meta's Code Llama (https://ai.meta.com/blog/code-llama-large- language-model-coding/), for example, produces code and natural language about code from both code and natural language inputs."
  ]
}